# Module 0: Introduction

<h2 class="author">Part of <a href="http://eyesofpanda.com" target="_blank">Licia He</a></h2>

In this module, we will cover:
1. How I got into generative plotter paintings
2. Why I decided to make this course
3. What will this course cover
4. Course resources and notes


Welcome to the very first module of this course! I am thrilled to finally launch this course!

This module is an introductory module that goes through the background and basics of this course. Most of the content is covered in the video. Enjoy!

I want to highlight a couple of things I mentioned in the video.

